#: ../../docs/classes/class_textureprogress.rst:14
msgid ""
"Texture-based progress bar. Useful for loading screens and life or "
"stamina bars."
msgstr "基于纹理的进度条。对于加载画面、生命或耐力条很有用。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_textureprogress.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_textureprogress.rst:19
msgid ""
"TextureProgress works like :ref:`ProgressBar <class_ProgressBar>`, but "
"uses up to 3 textures instead of Godot's :ref:`Theme <class_Theme>` "
"resource. It can be used to create horizontal, vertical and radial "
"progress bars."
msgstr ""
"``TextureProgress`` 的工作方式类似于 :ref:`ProgressBar "
"<class_ProgressBar>`，但是最多使用3个纹理而不是Godot的 :ref:`Theme <class_Theme>` "
"资源。它可用于创建水平、垂直和径向进度条。"

