"**FILL_RIGHT_TO_LEFT** = **1** --- The :ref:`texture_progress "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>` fills from right to "
"left."
msgstr ""
"**FILL_RIGHT_TO_LEFT** = **1** —— :ref:`texture_progress "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>` 从右到左填充。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_textureprogress.rst:96
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**FILL_TOP_TO_BOTTOM** = **2** --- The :ref:`texture_progress "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>` fills from top to "
"bottom."
msgstr ""
"**FILL_TOP_TO_BOTTOM** = **2** —— :ref:`texture_progress "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>` 从上到下填充。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_textureprogress.rst:98
msgid ""
"**FILL_BOTTOM_TO_TOP** = **3** --- The :ref:`texture_progress "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>` fills from bottom to "
"top."
msgstr ""
"**FILL_BOTTOM_TO_TOP** = **3** —— :ref:`texture_progress "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>` 从下到上填充。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_textureprogress.rst:100
msgid ""
"**FILL_CLOCKWISE** = **4** --- Turns the node into a radial bar. The "
":ref:`texture_progress <class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>`"
" fills clockwise. See :ref:`radial_center_offset "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_radial_center_offset>`, "
":ref:`radial_initial_angle "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_radial_initial_angle>` and "
":ref:`radial_fill_degrees "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_radial_fill_degrees>` to control the way "
"the bar fills up."
msgstr ""
"**FILL_CLOCKWISE** = **4** —— 将节点变成径向条。:ref:`texture_progress "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>` 顺时针填充。参见 "
":ref:`radial_center_offset "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_radial_center_offset>`、:ref:`radial_initial_angle"
" <class_TextureProgress_property_radial_initial_angle>` 和 "
":ref:`radial_fill_degrees "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_radial_fill_degrees>` 以控制条形填充的方式。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_textureprogress.rst:102
msgid ""
"**FILL_COUNTER_CLOCKWISE** = **5** --- Turns the node into a radial bar. "
"The :ref:`texture_progress "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>` fills "
"counterclockwise. See :ref:`radial_center_offset "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_radial_center_offset>`, "
":ref:`radial_initial_angle "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_radial_initial_angle>` and "
":ref:`radial_fill_degrees "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_radial_fill_degrees>` to control the way "
"the bar fills up."
msgstr ""
"**FILL_COUNTER_CLOCKWISE** = **5** —— 将节点变成径向条。:ref:`texture_progress "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>` 逆时针填充。参见 "
":ref:`radial_center_offset "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_radial_center_offset>`、:ref:`radial_initial_angle"
" <class_TextureProgress_property_radial_initial_angle>` 和 "
":ref:`radial_fill_degrees "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_radial_fill_degrees>` 以控制条形填充的方式。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_textureprogress.rst:104
msgid ""
"**FILL_BILINEAR_LEFT_AND_RIGHT** = **6** --- The :ref:`texture_progress "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>` fills from the center,"
" expanding both towards the left and the right."
msgstr ""
"**FILL_BILINEAR_LEFT_AND_RIGHT** = **6** —— :ref:`texture_progress "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>` 从中心填充，向左和向右同时扩展。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_textureprogress.rst:106
msgid ""
"**FILL_BILINEAR_TOP_AND_BOTTOM** = **7** --- The :ref:`texture_progress "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>` fills from the center,"
" expanding both towards the top and the bottom."
msgstr ""
"**FILL_BILINEAR_TOP_AND_BOTTOM** = **7** —— :ref:`texture_progress "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>` 从中心填充，向上和向下同时扩展。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_textureprogress.rst:108
msgid ""
"**FILL_CLOCKWISE_AND_COUNTER_CLOCKWISE** = **8** --- Turns the node into "
"a radial bar. The :ref:`texture_progress "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>` fills radially from "
"the center, expanding both clockwise and counterclockwise. See "
":ref:`radial_center_offset "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_radial_center_offset>`, "
":ref:`radial_initial_angle "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_radial_initial_angle>` and "
":ref:`radial_fill_degrees "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_radial_fill_degrees>` to control the way "
"the bar fills up."
msgstr ""
"**FILL_CLOCKWISE_AND_COUNTER_CLOCKWISE** = **8** —— "
"将节点变成一个径向条。:ref:`texture_progress "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_texture_progress>` 从中心径向填充，顺时针和逆时针扩展。参见 "
":ref:`radial_center_offset "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_radial_center_offset>`、:ref:`radial_initial_angle"
" <class_TextureProgress_property_radial_initial_angle>` 和 "
":ref:`radial_fill_degrees "
"<class_TextureProgress_property_radial_fill_degrees>` 以控制条形填充的方式。"

